INSERT INTO `tb_posts` (`post_id`, `post_type`, `post_title`, `post_content`, `post_isbreaking`, `post_image`, `post_author`, `post_date`) VALUES
(1, 'Campus News', 'Welcome to School', '<p>Whether you&#39;re a new student starting at a new school, or a returning student excited for another year of learning, welcome! This is a time for new beginnings, new challenges, and new opportunities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>School is a place where you can learn and grow academically, emotionally, and socially. It&#39;s a place where you can make new friends, discover new passions, and prepare for your future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As you start this new school year, here are a few tips to help you make the most of it:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Get involved.</strong>&nbsp;There are many ways to get involved at school, such as joining clubs, sports teams, or student government. Getting involved is a great way to meet new people, learn new skills, and make a difference in your community.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Be open-minded.</strong>&nbsp;School is a great time to explore different subjects and learn about different cultures. Be open to trying new things and learning from others.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Ask for help when you need it.</strong>&nbsp;There are many people at school who are there to help you succeed, including your teachers, counselors, and classmates. Don&#39;t be afraid to ask for help if you&#39;re struggling.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Have fun!</strong>&nbsp;School is a time to learn and grow, but it&#39;s also a time to have fun. Make sure to enjoy your time at school and make the most of all the opportunities it has to offer.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are some additional tips for making the most of the welcome back to school season:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Get to know your teachers.</strong>&nbsp;Take some time during the first few weeks of school to get to know your teachers. This will help you feel more comfortable in their classes and make it easier to ask for help when you need it.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Organize your school supplies.</strong>&nbsp;Having a well-organized workspace can help you stay focused and productive in class. Take some time to organize your school supplies and create a study space that works for you.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Set goals for yourself.</strong>&nbsp;What do you want to achieve this school year? Once you know your goals, you can start to make a plan to achieve them.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Get involved in extracurricular activities.</strong>&nbsp;Extracurricular activities are a great way to meet new people, learn new skills, and have fun. There are many different extracurricular activities to choose from, so find something that interests you and get involved.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Welcome to school! We hope you have a great year.</p>\r\n', 'No', '20231013-erere.jpg', 'Fortune', '2023-10-13 04:53:09'),
(2, 'Campus News', 'Payment of SUG fee', '<p>The Students&#39; Union Government (<strong>SUG</strong>) is the official representative body of students in an educational institution. It is responsible for protecting the rights and interests of students, and for providing them with a platform to express their views and concerns.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The SUG fee is a compulsory levy paid by all students to support the activities of the union. This fee is used to fund a variety of student services, such as:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Scholarships and bursaries</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Student clubs and societies</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Sports and recreational activities</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Welfare and counseling services</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Advocacy and representation</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The SUG fee can be paid online or in person at the SUG office. The exact payment procedure may vary depending on the institution, but it is typically a straightforward process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>To pay your SUG fee online:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><em>Visit the SUG website or online payment portal.</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Create an account or log in to your existing account.</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Select the payment option you prefer and enter the required information.</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Review your payment details and confirm the transaction.</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>You will receive a confirmation receipt once your payment is successful.</em></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>To pay your SUG fee in person:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><em>Visit the SUG office during business hours.</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Bring your student ID card and the required amount of cash or debit card.</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Fill out a payment form and submit it to the SUG cashier.</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>You will receive a receipt for your payment.</em></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Payment deadlines</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The deadline for paying the SUG fee varies depending on the institution. However, most institutions require students to pay their fees by the end of the first semester. Students who fail to pay their SUG fees by the deadline may be subject to late fees or other penalties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Importance of paying the SUG fee</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The SUG fee is an important source of funding for the Students&#39; Union Government. It allows the union to provide students with a variety of services that would not otherwise be possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Paying your SUG fee is also a way to show your support for the union and its work. The SUG is a student-led organization that is dedicated to representing the interests of all students. By paying your SUG fee, you are helping to ensure that the union has the resources it needs to continue its important work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Conclusion</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The payment of SUG fee is an important responsibility for all students. By paying your SUG fee, you are supporting the union&#39;s work to protect your rights and interests, and to provide you with a variety of valuable services.</p>\r\n', 'Yes', 'default.jpg', 'Rasheed', '2023-10-13 06:50:55'),
(3, 'Applied Science', 'NACOS Workshop Update', '<p><strong>Empowering the Future: Discovering your tech identity</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Join us for a workshop on Wednesday, October 4, 2023, where you will learn how to discover and embrace your tech identity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this workshop, you will:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Explore what it means to have a tech identity</li>\r\n	<li>Identify your unique strengths and skills</li>\r\n	<li>Develop a plan to achieve your tech career goals</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>This workshop is perfect for anyone who is interested in a career in tech, regardless of their experience level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you are a student, a recent graduate, or a seasoned professional, this workshop will help you take your tech career to the next level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Register today at [registration link]</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>#techidentity #workshop #professionaldevelopment</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Personal touch:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I&#39;m passionate about helping people discover and embrace their tech identity because I believe that everyone has something unique to offer the tech industry. In this workshop, I&#39;ll share my own journey to finding my tech identity and teach you the tools and resources you need to find yours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Call to action:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Register today and learn how to empower your future by discovering your tech identity!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also add a relevant quote or statistic to your post to make it more visually appealing and engaging. For example, you could add something like:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&quot;The future belongs to those who believe in the beauty of their dreams.&quot; - Eleanor Roosevelt</li>\r\n	<li>&quot;The global tech industry is expected to grow by 10% in the next five years.&quot; - International Data Corporation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Be sure to tailor your post to your target audience. For example, if you are targeting students, you could mention how the workshop can help them prepare for a career in tech. If you are targeting professionals, you could mention how the workshop can help them advance their careers.</p>\r\n', 'Yes', '20231013-socialmeta.jpg', 'Joshua', '2023-10-13 07:06:08');
